Class HeapPropertiesTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.storage.heap.tuple.HeapDataTuple
      • com.gridgraph.storage.heap.tuple.HeapPropertiesTuple
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EdgePropertiesTuple, VertexPropertiesTuple

    public abstract class HeapPropertiesTuple
extends HeapDataTuple
    An HeapPropertiesTuple represents binary data for properties data of a graph element, read from and written to file or mapped memory
